4c1.45 0 3-1.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>3-2 root-context.xml 설정</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>어떤 DB를 선택해서 연결할거냐를 설정해줘야 합니다.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>유튜브 강의에서는 servlet-context.xml에서 설정하는데, 구글링 해보니까 root-context.xml에 설정하는게 일반적인 것 같아요.</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>네임스페이스 탭 클릭 -> aop, beans, context, jdbc, mybatis-spring 클릭</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Source 탭으로 돌아와서 다음 코드 입력</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"xml\"><pre class=\"language-xml\"><code class=\"language-xml\"><span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- root-context.xml --></span>\n\n    <span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- namespace 부분 생략 --></span>\n\n\t<span class=\"token comment\">&lt;!-- 1. DB Connection을 위한 객체 생성 --></span>\n    <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>bean</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">id</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>dataSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">class</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>org.springframework.jdbc.datasource.DriverManagerDataSource<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span>\n      <span class=\"token attr-name\">lazy-init</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>false<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span><span class=\"token punctuation\">></span></span>\n        <span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token tag\"><span class=\"token punctuation\">&lt;</span>property</span> <span class=\"token attr-name\">name</span><span class=\"token attr-value\"><span class=\"token punctuation attr-equals\">=</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span>driverClassName<span class=\"token punctuation\">\"</span></span> <s